  "title": "Mild Turkish Mushroom Kebabs",
  "description": "A quick and flavorful Turkish dish featuring mushrooms, perfect for a paleo-friendly meal, with a smoky and slightly briny taste. This recipe is easy to prepare and can be ready in under 30 minutes.",
