  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the mushrooms to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the mushrooms onto skewers, leaving a small space between each mushroom.",
    "Grill the mushrooms for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until they are tender and slightly charred.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
